        <div class="info-step">
          <div class="info-step__num">01</div>
          <h3 class="info-step__title">Measure Your Space</h3>
          <p>Measure all doorways, stairwells, landings, and hallways our team will need to navigate. Standard beds require at least 75cm clearance.</p>
