        <div class="info-step">
          <div class="info-step__num">02</div>
          <h3 class="info-step__title">Clear the Route</h3>
          <p>Remove rugs, wall art, and any furniture that may obstruct the path to your bedroom. A clear route means a faster, damage-free delivery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-step">
          <div class="info-step__num">03</div>
          <h3 class="info-step__title">Be Available</h3>
          <p>Ensure someone aged 18 or over is present to accept delivery. Our drivers will call ahead on the day with a 2-hour delivery window.</p>
